Package: metaverse
Title: Versatile Evidence Synthesis with Robust Estimation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mahmood Ahmad [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Mahmood Ahmad <mahmood.ahmad@example.com>
Authors@R:
    person("Mahmood", "Ahmad", email = "mahmood.ahmad@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for robust meta-analysis implementing
    cutting-edge statistical methods including contamination models, knockoff
    filters, spike-and-slab priors, conformal prediction, and causal inference
    helpers. The package provides robust estimation by default, handles
    dependent effect sizes, and includes extensive sensitivity analysis
    workflows. Features include publication bias detection, influence
    diagnostics, transportability analysis, and publication-quality
    visualization tools.
